BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: TorontoBabel Language Exchange
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/torontobabel/
UID:event_313055109@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260316T030231Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260318T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260318T230000
SUMMARY:Language Exchange & Social by Toronto Babel: Spring Equinox (Nowru
 z edition)
DESCRIPTION:TorontoBabel: Toronto's International Language Exchange\n**Spr
 ing Equinox: A Nowruz Partnership**\n\nThis week\, we are honoured to part
 ner with friends from the Persian community for a special evening centered
  around **Nowruz** (the Persian New Year) and the arrival of Spring.\nWhil
 e Toronto Babel is always a place for all languages\, tonight we’re exci
 ted to share the "soul" of this culture through their famous traditions an
 d timeless poetry.\n✨ **What to Expect:**\n✅ **The Haft-Seen Tradition
 :** We will have a traditional display of the seven symbolic items of spri
 ng. Come learn what they represent for renewal and hope.\n✅**Poetry & Fo
 rtunes:** We’ll be sharing snippets of **Hafez**. In this culture\, poet
 ry isn't just art\, it's a way to seek guidance and connection.\n✅**Lang
 uage Bites:** We’ll have a few key Farsi words and phrases on hand to he
 lp you navigate the night and connect with our Persian members.\n\n📍 14
  Madison Ave\, Toronto\, ON M5R 2S1\n🕖 7:00 PM – 11:00 PM\n\n💵 $5 
 Entry Fee at the Door\nThis helps cover meetup essentials and all the litt
 le things that make our events magical ✨\n\n**CONTACT:** Terry (Organize
 r)\n📲 E-transfer also available: tmg8@wealthsimple.me\n🔗 Meetup: [ht
 tps://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel](https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel)\n
 📘 Facebook: [https://www.facebook.com/groups/torontobabel](https://www.
 facebook.com/groups/torontobabel)\n💬 WhatsApp: [https://chat.whatsapp.c
 om/EYMdUw8XaxE5irFSNg5bt7](https://chat.whatsapp.com/EYMdUw8XaxE5irFSNg5bt
 7)\n📸 Instagram: [https://www.instagram.com/t.o.babel](https://www.inst
 agram.com/t.o.babel)\n\n👉 Check out our calendar to see what other even
 ts we have coming up and to RSVP:\n[https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel/#c
 alendar](https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel/#calendar)\n\n**Note:** Toron
 to Babel is a friendly\, welcoming\, and safe space for all attendees. Thi
 s is a language-focused event and not a dating or matchmaking event. Any f
 orm of harassment or inappropriate behavior will not be tolerated. If you 
 experience or witness any issues\, please inform one of the organizers.\n\
 n#TorontoBabel #LanguageExchange #TorontoEvents #ToDoToronto #LearnEnglish
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/torontobabel/events/313055109/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260125T220759Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260125T220759Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: TorontoBabel Language Exchange
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/torontobabel/
UID:event_313754245@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260316T030231Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260321T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260321T230000
SUMMARY:Toronto Babel: Spring Break Edition @ Condo Party Room 
DESCRIPTION:TorontoBabel: Toronto's International Language Exchange\n**Eve
 nt Space & Toronto Babel Presents: 🌴 Spring Break — Toronto Edition 
 ☀️**\n\nJoin us for a special Saturday night in our brand new condo pa
 rty room with two rooms near College St & McCaul St.\n\nSpring is almost h
 ere\, and we’re bringing the vacation vibes to you! Think bright shirts\
 , summer anthems\, and a room full of people ready to kick off spring the 
 fun way as we turn our party room space into a mini Spring Break escape—
 complete with inflatable beach balls\, tropical fits\, a DJ spinning class
 ic summer throwbacks all night\, and karaoke sing-alongs in the second roo
 m. 🌴☀️🎶\n\nSo throw on your loudest floral shirt or most colourf
 ul summer fit and come ready for a night of music\, drinks\, and great com
 pany.\n\n**✨ What to Expect:**\n🎧 DJ F.L.Ÿ spinning Summer Anthem Cl
 assics\n🎤 Karaoke sing-alongs in the second room\n🏖️ Spring Break 
 theme & décor\n🍹 Drinks\, snacks & great social vibes\n\n**🎟️ Tic
 kets:**\n💸 $20 general admission – Includes **1 complimentary alcohol
 ic or non-alcoholic drink**\nAdditional drink tickets will be available fo
 r purchase. **No outside alcohol permitted.**\n\nUse Code 'BL05' - Get you
 r tickets here: [https://www.event-space.net/event-details/spring-break-to
 ronto-edition](https://www.event-space.net/event-details/spring-break-toro
 nto-edition)\n\n📍 Location available with online ticket - College St & 
 McCaul St\n\n**📅 Saturday\, March 21**\n**⏰ 6 PM – 11 PM**\n\n**⚠
 ️ Limited capacity — advance tickets required. Our last Lunar Event So
 ld Out.**\n\nNo flights\, no passports—just Spring Break energy in the h
 eart of Toronto. 🌴🎉
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/torontobabel/events/313754245/
